{"id":232977181,"title":"#問 ASUS筆電","content":"我的筆電有4年了，但都只用來文書處理。\n（只做 word類 跟 ppt類 的報告）\n偶爾會拿來看影片\n但只要不連電源，它就會像影片那樣；\n無預警關機並且無限開機關機，\n還會發出「喀」的怪聲⋯\n\n這個狀況持續有快半年多了吧\n本來頻率沒那麼頻繁 久久一次\n到現在幾乎都要連著充電器。\n\n1個禮拜前有送修，昨天才拿回來\n華碩那邊表示是電池問題\n所以幫我更換電池（過保固了，2565元）\n\n結果剛剛使用不到10分鐘\n又開始了⋯⋯\n\n想請問有沒有了解或有這方面經驗的卡友\n可以諮詢建議呢？\n\n目前因為家境不是很寬裕\n應該不考慮換一台新的\n\n先磕頭感謝了🙇🏻‍♀️🙇🏻‍♀️\n\n————\n\n影片在此：\nhttps://www.dcard.tw/v2/vivid/videos/001eb192-4e3a-4fab-9574-6419da5c4d6e?r=0.5625","excerpt":"我的筆電有4年了，但都只用來文書處理。（只做 word類 跟 ppt類 的報告），偶爾會拿來看影片，但只要不連電源，它就會像影片那樣；無預警關機並且無限開機關機，還會發出「喀」的怪聲⋯，這個狀況持續有","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"0e0bc27b-8c69-4149-b229-04e7a865a09d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-29T07:46:12.872Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T07:46:12.872Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":4,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["筆電","ASUS","電腦"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"3C","forumAlias":"3c","school":"康寧大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":true,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c28ef175-8b2e-455a-bee6-8be4e391c8b6","url":"https://www.dcard.tw/v2/vivid/videos/001eb192-4e3a-4fab-9574-6419da5c4d6e?r=0.5625","normalizedUrl":"","thumbnail":"https://vivid.dcard.tw/Public/001eb192-4e3a-4fab-9574-6419da5c4d6e/thumbnail.jpg","type":"video/vivid","tags":["ANNOTATED_FAILED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-29T07:46:12.872Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T07:46:12.872Z"}],"postAvatar":""}